**Key Notes**

-   All mentors have data plans, but connection quality varies -
    > offline-first or "save and sync later" mode is ideal

-   Photos: continue via WhatsApp unless reliable upload is confirmed

-   Language: English and Xitsonga side-by-side

-   Access Levels: mentors can submit only; staff can view/edit/export

-   Testing: led by Becky, Trygive, and Quentan

